sentences: Founded in 1983, the Rönninge Show Chorus is one of the largest and most successful a cappella choruses in Scandinavia.
Rönninge have represented Sweden in SAI's international chorus competition for over 20 years, never placing lower than 6th in the world.
They are the 2014 SAI international gold medal chorus, having achieved that honor at the 2013 contest in Honolulu, HI, with a score of 3138 out of a possible 3280.

Britt-Helene Bonnedahl has been involved in barbershop singing since 1976 and has been part of the Rönninge Show Chorus since its inception.
She has been a member of the international faculty for Sweet Adelines International for many years and her musical influence is felt throughout the world of barbershop music.
